<subSubSection id="B6181691B5BDD44234E8070DC76577D9" pageId="7" pageNumber="92" type="distribution">
<paragraph id="97197D03036DB321A906E48C293097D4" pageId="7" pageNumber="92">Habit, ecology and distribution.</paragraph>
<paragraph id="24FA68DFE16CE85EE3ACBE309E61187F" pageId="7" pageNumber="92">Solitary, scattered on soil in broadleaf forests and mixed forests; currently only known from China.</paragraph>
</subSubSection>
